g.text: We foster collaboraton among development, security, and operatons teams from the project's incepton.
We implement robust CI/CD pipelines to automate testng, deployment, and security checks.
Security is not an aferthought; it's an integral part of our development process.
We leverage Infrastructure as Code principles to ensure consistent and secure infrastructure deployments.
Our DevSecOps model includes contnuous monitoring of applicatons and infrastructure.
